{"tid":1864094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求幫推] 致還未罷工醫護專職手足","createTime":"2020-02-05T12:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T06:33:22.000Z","uid":78857,"like":91,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"88a0400991661c2e2f72164e956491d3cb9d1c01","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"想同所有人講 唔單止係醫護同事手足<br />\n琴日同今日已經有超過7000位醫護專職<br />\n為香港放低一直以黎ge道德枷鎖<br />\n冒著被秋後 被打壓 行到最前去罷工<br />\n如果仍在考慮ge你 跪求請你再三思<br />\n香港真係危在旦夕 人傳人 已經出現<br />\n社區爆發只係一步之遙<br />\n求下你地 再考慮下&hellip;<br />\n唔罷曬咁多日 罷一日都好<br />\n唔真罷工 考慮下SL&hellip;&hellip;幾多日都好<br />\n同埋最起碼唔好去頂更..去賺SHS&hellip;"},{"pid":"55d5c9cf21c85e7402f6385136630fa03051c462","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fcc080177293d067d3af280341744086b571337","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"第2次POST ...求幫推"},{"pid":"cef1dfafe049bc9b1c2c9718ba033d4636844f37","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d172ba1f58b5414dba7c3bd71778f765a9feb0f4","tid":1864094,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:22:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2c389cef60ef2b235b8317d8319c14917487d8c","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"第2次POST ...求幫推"},{"pid":"d9422af798237be930fa3afb08aaa5ed25c7a2e7","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"第2次POST ...求幫推"},{"pid":"cd33f7f7708e961478c34111dee2fc9f8274e042","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"第2次POST ...求幫推"},{"pid":"76dab54ec5baa3fb2f284d07d73e1e866eb8cce9","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy