 香港人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eQoLAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eQoLAS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於太多吹風唔罷<br />\n我想講既係醫護罷工起左個頭後，好多工會都準備緊<br />\n香港人要做既係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷</span></span></strong><br />\n直至政府做返本身佢應該要做既事，甚至係五大訴求<br />\n成個制度已經由內至外腐爛，一日唔改變都只會有同樣既事情發生<br />\n而唔係咩社區大爆發之後成班返去醫院醫病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護工會並不代表所有醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n<br />\n妥協只會失敗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWp8d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWp8d0.png&h=12ec3a53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bcbce62b77656fbe352b8f242d3e3b806363c85","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"第2次POST ...求幫推"},{"pid":"77508ec967488f49efed29d364ce4b30d290a748","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"第2次POST ...求幫推"},{"pid":"b33daa90a2daa5b704ef7bbf3c98ffd67fe9521f","tid":1864094,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"第2次POST ...求幫推"},{"pid":"3c2428a4d611deaaf0f2aca72012cb463ac3a1da","tid":1864094,"uid":273716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"仲唔罷既，就同藍絲醫護齊上齊落<br />\n準備上前線，做中華英雄，為國捐軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f00e431c8742bfc060f60c068d2c10ea431b39a","tid":1864094,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"希望更多醫護可以走出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b995c1e7cbda